---
title: Rules for Buying Your First Firearm for Home Defense and Range Time
description: >-
  Essential guidelines and legal requirements for purchasing your first firearm
  for home defense in Virginia and the surrounding areas.
---
1. **Your gun needs to look like a gun.** \
   No bright or “cute” colors (pink, purple, Tiffany blue, etc.). Stick to practical, professional colors: black, gunmetal gray, olive green, flat dark earth, or tan.

1. **5 or fewer major parts (field-strip level).** \
   Frame, recoil spring, barrel, slide, and magazine. You should never need to disassemble the gun beyond basic field stripping for cleaning.

1. **Striker-fired only (no external hammers).** \
   Consistent trigger pull every single time.

1. **Largest frame that still fits your hand comfortably.** \
   Go compact or full-size. Bigger guns are easier to shoot well, especially under stress or during longer range sessions.

1. **Single-stack or double-stack (your choice).** \
   Double-stack gives you higher capacity but a thicker grip. Single-stack is slimmer and easier for smaller hands but holds fewer rounds.

1. **Price range: $400 – $700.** \
   If it’s well under $400 or well over $700, you should understand why (used gun, includes optic, special edition, etc.).

1. **Stick to proven major manufacturers.** \
   Top reliable brands: Ruger, Sig Sauer, Smith & Wesson, Glock, Beretta, Remington, Heckler & Koch (H&K), Benelli, and Walther.

1. **Zero or one external safety only.** \
   External safeties are mechanical devices that can fail or be forgotten under stress. Prefer guns with a grip safety, a simple thumb safety, or no external safety at all.

1. **Where to buy in the Northern Virginia area**

   - **Ashburn, VA**: Silver Eagle Group – [https://silvereaglegroup.com/](https://silvereaglegroup.com/)
   - **Manassas, VA**: Trojan Arms & Tactical – [https://www.trojanarmsinc.com/](https://www.trojanarmsinc.com/)

1. **Get quality training regularly.** \
   Professional instruction is the most important part of responsible ownership. Visit [Live Fire Instruction](https://livefireinstruction.com) (Northern Virginia’s premier firearms training company, right here in NOVA) – [https://livefireinstruction.com/](https://livefireinstruction.com/)

